com.bizosys.hsearch.index
Class TermType

java.lang.Object
  com.bizosys.hsearch.index.TermType

public class TermType
extends java.lang.Object

Defines various term types. To save indexing space, each term type is stored as a byte code. So totally 256 diffierent codes can be defined in the existing index.
